      • getQueue

        public java.util.List<com.sedmelluq.discord.lavaplayer.track.AudioTrack> getQueue()
        Returns the queue for this scheduler. Adding to the head of the queue (index 0) does not automatically cause it to start playing immediately. The returned collection is thread-safe and can be modified.

        To iterate over this queue, use a synchronized block. For example: synchronize (formatQueueOutput()) { // iteration code }
